title: Counter-Strike.Source-2017.v89-Autoupdate-Multilanguage-FULL
description:
Description

About Counter-Strike: Source:
===============

NEXT PART OF THE WORLD №1 ONLINE EXCELLENT GAME,
Counter-Strike: Source blends the award-winning Counter-Strike team game with Advanced ™ Engine technology.
Including improved graphic design, new sounds and physics input, Counter-Strike: Source is a must for any action
gamer.


System Requirements:

Minimum: 1.7GHz processor, 512MB RAM, DirectX® 8.1 graphics
card (requires SSE support), Windows® 7 (32/64-bit) / Vista / XP, mouse, keyboard,

Recommended: Pentium 4
processor (3.0 GHz or better), 1GB RAM, DirectX® 9 graphics card, Windows® 7 (32/64-bit) / Vista / XP, mouse,
keyboard,

Installation:
=============


1. Start Counter-Strike-Source.v89.exe
2. Select a language
3. Follow the
installer's steps
4. Once the installation is complete, CSS-Updater.exe will download the new game update if
available. Please do not interrupt this process.

====================
To change your name, type in the
game console: setname "your nick here"
====================


Updating support:
====================

If you can not connect to servers newer than the game, please run: CSS-Updater.exe
again and the game will be updated to the latest version.
